Daniel Pollock https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daniel_Pollock 0 Daniel John Pollock (24 August 1968 – 13 April 1992) was an Australian actor best known for his role as Davey in the 1992 Australian drama film Romper Stomper, which featured Russell Crowe.
